structure.unit: COUNTY ROAD ENGINEER AND MAINTENANCE OF PUBLIC ROADS

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 218, sec. 15, effective July 1, 1980. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 140, sec. 2, effective June 16, 1960. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 4308-4, 4308-5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Department of highways to direct expenditures -- Prescribe rules.
